msgctxt "sn46.47:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 46"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 46"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn46.47:0.2"
msgid "5. Cakkavattivagga"
msgstr "5. A Wheel Turning Monarch"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 47. Adaliddasutta → adaḷiddasuttaṃ (bj) | adaliddo (pts1)
msgctxt "sn46.47:0.3"
msgid "47. Adaliddasutta"
msgstr "47. Prosperous"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
#. VAR: Adaliddo, adaliddo’ti → adaḷiddo adaḷiddoti (bj, s1-3)
msgctxt "sn46.47:1.1"
msgid "“‘Adaliddo, adaliddo’ti, bhante, vuccati."
msgstr "“Sir, they speak of someone who is ‘prosperous’."

msgctxt "sn46.47:1.2"
msgid "Kittāvatā nu kho, bhante, ‘adaliddo’ti vuccatī”ti?"
msgstr "How is a prosperous person defined?”"

msgctxt "sn46.47:1.3"
msgid ""
"“Sattannaṃ kho, bhikkhu, bojjhaṅgānaṃ bhāvitattā bahulīkatattā ‘adaliddo’ti "
"vuccati."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicant, they’re called prosperous because they’ve developed and "
"cultivated the seven awakening factors."

msgctxt "sn46.47:1.4"
msgid "Katamesaṃ sattannaṃ?"
msgstr "What seven?"

msgctxt "sn46.47:1.5"
msgid "Satisambojjhaṅgassa … pe … upekkhāsambojjhaṅgassa—"
msgstr ""
"The awakening factors of mindfulness, investigation of principles, energy, "
"rapture, tranquility, immersion, and equanimity."

msgctxt "sn46.47:1.6"
msgid ""
"imesaṃ kho, bhikkhu, sattannaṃ bojjhaṅgānaṃ bhāvitattā bahulīkatattā "
"‘adaliddo’ti vuccatī”ti."
msgstr ""
"They’re called prosperous because they’ve developed and cultivated these "
"seven awakening factors.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn46.47:1.7"
msgid "Sattamaṃ."
msgstr ""
